    "Many tools integrate multiple data modalities (e.g.",
    "sequence, structure and expression) and can operate across different cell types and organisms.",
    "AI tools for predicting phenotypic characteristics of pathogens from genomic and structural data.",
    "We define pathogen property prediction tools to be AI models that predict phenotypic characteristics of pathogens including virulence and antimicrobial resistance.",
    "These tools use various machine learning approaches, including deep learning, to analyse pathogen sequences and structures."
